title: Last match doesn't show up
body:
Hello!
I just played as Vayne on bot with my friend who was support.I was very fed because in the enemy team there was a troller,at the end of the game my lol client freezes,I logged in again and my last match was not in my match history.
Can somebody help me?
  Thanks!

replies.body:
Hey there,

This issue is currently being investigated by Riot, it should be resolved soon.

Edit: Update, the issue has been resolved & match history should be caught up in a few hours.
